            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to create the modern Ferrari 250 GT SWB California Spider, however it has to be a Ferrari and not a vehicle from another brand, for legal reasons. Trust us, you don’t want to cross Ferrari legally since the Italians aggressively defend their intellectual property.",
